{"tid":1709062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我要屌燒藍絲個位手足","createTime":"2019-11-11T21:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T23:23:32.000Z","uid":116074,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b852fb01aa8df3e71adcb4f34cd3660daedc98c","tid":1709062,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:45:21.000Z","msg":"前線決定，我從來唔盡信，正如人我唔信有十全十美既人性，亦同唔信黑警一樣，無有效制衡的武力必使人腐敗。<br />\n<br />\n我懇請各位，將手中既武力對準政權、警權、或保護手足，而非對付無即時威脅性既藍絲或尻扔。<br />\n<br />\n當惡變成平常，那又何故苦苦追尋善？<br />\n當只追尋勝利，我們或許不配擁有善。<br />\n<br />\n題外話：黎明到，去晨運。"},{"pid":"89546c747bd2e9d447318c488841b0201a8f25bd","tid":1709062,"uid":263391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:46:15.000Z","msg":"你知個藍絲做過乜？"},{"pid":"7a019e120bd567fbbf818f339972c16d1cc4df06","tid":1709062,"uid":43976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:47:08.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"1b144797121107e1c3e37eb6dfac62b4df160622","tid":1709062,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:47:31.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b7b09bc987392005070f3a4ce6d9bd5376df6b92","tid":1709062,"uid":329289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:48:39.000Z","msg":"總之前線做咩我地都唔會割 你條分化撚仲有咩野講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523e9c9392528dd7ffa66ca9781854c32bd24eb7","tid":1709062,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:49:29.000Z","msg":"掉左咁多次雞尾酒去d狗到你唔出聲？<br />\n<br />\n依家條友話自己係狗，重走去捉人，當狗處理好理所當然"},{"pid":"11d23508fe5edead25a88332a9a2c90a0fa84d7f","tid":1709062,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:51:19.000Z","msg":"唯一要譴責嘅野係冇燒死隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理佢係真係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c7927c9a9227b73860154f185d2fa96b283b1d","tid":1709062,"uid":213781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"